<item>
            <title>[SOLR-8712] Variable solr.core.instanceDir no longer resolved</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8712</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In 5.4.1 standalone mode it was possible to use &lt;tt&gt;${solr.core.instanceDir&lt;/tt&gt;} in the data import config file. This property is no longer available in 5.5.0. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12941060">SOLR-8712</key>
            <summary>Variable solr.core.instanceDir no longer resolved</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
