[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=lucene-solr.git;h=4e1c381&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=lucene-solr.git;h=4e1c381&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8712&quot; title=&quot;Variable solr.core.instanceDir no longer resolved&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-8712&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-8712&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Variable solr.core.instanceDir was not being resolved&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15170545" author="romseygeek" created="Sat, 27 Feb 2016 10:38:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed - thanks for raising the issue Kristine!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
